4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Course that helps students become web development experts. The course focuses on building applications from scratch and provides the necessary skills and technologies for a career in tech. It is an 18-week program, and students can choose between English and Spanish for the syllabus and content. The course includes three classes per week and has no prerequisites, making it suitable for those without coding skills or advanced math knowledge. Upon completion, students receive a Full-Stack Developer certificate. The program also emphasizes hands-on experience through project development and presentation. The instructors, Rodolfo Campos and Gabriel Salinas, bring their industry expertise to the course. For more information, visit the website at https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/part-time-full-stack-developer. stop